+
+        # Group items by acquisition date (solar day). Adjacent MGRS tiles in the
+        # same Sentinel-2 swath are captured in the same minute, so grouping by
+        # date is sufficient for mosaicing tile-boundary AOIs.
+        by_date = defaultdict(list)
